videoSnippet.title: Merry Christmas With a Wild Game from Ruslan Supermariov
videoSnippet.description:
#agadmator Merry Christmas Everyone! :)

Ruslan Ponomariov vs Ivan Sokolov
"Supermariov" (game of the day Jul-23-2014)
Ruy Lopez Festival (2007), Zafra ESP, rd 1, Mar-17 
Queen's Gambit Accepted: Central. Greco Variation (D20)

1. d4 d5 2. c4 dc4 3. e4 b5 4. a4 c6 5. ab5 cb5 6. Nc3 Bd7 7. Nf3 e6 8. Be2 Nf6 9. O-O Be7 10. d5 ed5 11. ed5 Qb6 12. Bf4 Bc5 13. Bc4 bc4 14. Qe2 Kf8 15. Ne5 Bf5 16. Na4 Qb5 17. Nc5 Qc5 18. Nc4 Qd4 19. Be5 Bd3 20. Qd2 Qd5 21. Rfd1 Qc4 22. Rac1 Qa6 23. Bf6 Nd7 24. Bc3 Bb5 25. Qg5 Nf6 26. Qc5 Kg8 27. Bf6 h6 28. Bc3 Re8 29. Rd6 Qb7 30. Qf5 Qe7 31. Qb5
